description: Joe Lovano sits down with Wayne Shorter for the final part of a discussion about music and beyond. Now available from Blue Note Records: Wayne Shorter Quartet's WITHOUT A NET (http://smarturl.it/WANiT) & Joe Lovano Us Five's CROSS CULTURE (http://smarturl.it/z2y0ko)
